OL,3,CMulti-million pound refurbishment to
OL,4,Cprovide demential care in the region
OL,6,FCouncil bosses in Cumbria say multi-
OL,7,Fmillion pound refurbishments to a
OL,8,FEskdale House will provide essential
OL,9,Fdementia care in the region.
OL,11,FWhile Eskdale House was renovated,
OL,12,Fsome residents were moved to Moot
OL,13,FLodge in Brampton, which is currently
OL,14,Funder threat of closure. A
OL,15,Fconsultation is ongoing.
OL,17,FThe council claim that the amount of
OL,18,Fmoney invested in Eskdale House
OL,19,Fwouldn't have been able to bring Moot
OL,20,FLodge up to the same standard needed
OL,21,Ffor dementia care.
