OL,6,FThe refurbishment of the 21-bed care
OL,7,Fhome includes upgrades and
OL,8,Fimprovements to facilities, with a
OL,9,Ffocus on dementia care and
OL,10,Fsustainability.
OL,12,FAfter two years, the care home is
OL,13,Fexpected to welcome back resident soon.
OL,15,FCouncillor Lisa Brown, Executive
OL,16,FMember for Adults and Community
OL,17,FHealth, said: "We're thrilled to
OL,18,Funveil the newly refurbished Eskdale
OL,19,FHouse.
