OL,6,F"This project reflects Cumberland
OL,7,FCouncil's commitment to modernising
OL,8,Fcare facilities.
OL,10,F"With #2.3 million invested, Eskdale
OL,11,FHouse now offers excellent dementia
OL,12,Fcare in a safe and accessible
OL,13,Fenvironment.
OL,15,F"The redesigned spaces promote
OL,16,Fsocialisation and independence for
OL,17,Fresidents, while also supporting our
OL,18,Fdedicated staff in delivering high-
OL,19,Fquality care."
